04111005051679|title=\u2018\ub8e8\uac08\u2019 \ucd5c\uc9c4\ud601\u2192\uc870\ub3d9\ud601, \ub354 \uac15\ub825\ud574\uc9c4 4\u4eba \ud300\ud50c\ub808\uc774\u2026\uc0c8 \ubbf8\uc158 \ub098\uc120\ub2e4|website=\ud55c\uad6d\uc77c\ubcf4|language=ko|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref> It was also premiere on [[Netflix]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kof.inven.co.kr/dataninfo/fighter/?code=21200|title=\ud0b9 \uc624\ube0c \ud30c\uc774\ud130 \uc62c\uc2a4\ud0c0 \uc778\ubca4 - AS \ubc14\ub2e5\uc744 \ubaa8\ub974\ub294 \uc695\ub9dd\uc758 \ub8e8\uac08|website=kof.inven.co.kr|language=ko|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.joins.com/article/23562272|title=[\ub2e8\ub3c5]\ucd5c\uc9c4\ud601\u00b7\ubc15\uc131\uc6c5, OCN '\ub8e8\uac08' \uc8fc\uc778\uacf5|last=\uc785\ub825 2019.08.26 17:31|date=2019-08-26|website=\uc911\uc559\uc77c\ubcf4|language=ko|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newspim.com/news/view/20200327000787|title='\ub8e8\uac08' '\ucee4\ubba4\ub2c8\ud2f0' '\uc624\uc790\ud06c3'\u2026\ub137\ud50c\ub9ad\uc2a4, \uc774\ubc88\uc8fc \uc2e0\uc791 \ub77c\uc778\uc5c5 \uacf5\uac1c|date=2020-03-27|website=\ub274\uc2a4\ud54c|language=ko|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Rugal\n| image                    = Rugal poster.jpg\n| caption                  = Promotional poster\n| show_name_2              = \n| native_name              = {{Infobox name module|hangul=\ub8e8\uac08}}\n| genre                    = {{ubl|[[Thriller]]|[[Action]]|[[Crime]]}}\n| creator                  = \n| based_on                 = Webtoon by Rilmae\n| developer                = \n| writer                   = Do Hyun\n| director                 = Kang Cheol Woo\n| starring                 = {{ubl|[[Choi Jin-hyuk]]|[[Park Sung-woong]]|[[Park Sun-ho]]|[[Jo Dong-hyuk]]|Jung Hye-in|Kim Min-sang}}\n| theme_music_composer     = \n| opentheme                = \n| endtheme                 = \n| composer                 = \n| countr