 \ub098\ud0c0\ub09c \u2018\uc2e4\ud5d8\uccb4\u2019 \uae40\ub2e4\ud604|date=2020-04-12|website=hankyung.com|language=ko|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n== Cast ==\n\n=== Main ===\n\u2022 [[Choi Jin-hyuk]] as Kang Gi Bum<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/ko-kr/entertainment/tv/%EB%A3%A8%EA%B0%88-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A7%84%ED%98%81-%EB%B0%95%EC%84%B1%EC%9B%85%E3%83%BB%ED%95%9C%EC%A7%80%EC%99%84%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A9%B4-%EB%8F%8C%ED%8C%8C%ED%8D%BC%ED%8E%99%ED%8A%B8-%ED%9E%88%EC%96%B4%EB%A1%9C/ar-BB12uUUX|title='\ub8e8\uac08' \ucd5c\uc9c4\ud601, \ubc15\uc131\uc6c5\u30fb\ud55c\uc9c0\uc644\uc5d0 \uc815\uba74 \ub3cc\ud30c..\ud37c\ud399\ud2b8 \ud788\uc5b4\ub85c|website=www.msn.com|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n\u2022 [[Park Sung-woong]] as Hwang Deuk Goo\n\n\u2022 [[Park Sun-ho]] as Lee Gwang Cheol\n\n\u2022 [[Jung Hae-in|Jung Hye-in]] as Song Mi Na\n\n\u2022 [[Jo Dong-hyuk]] as Han Tae Woong\n\n\u2022 Kim Min-sang as Choi Geun Cheol\n\n\u2022 Han Ji Wan as Choi Ye Won\n\n=== Supporting ===\n\u2022 [[Jang In-sub|Jang In Sub]] as Bradley [Rugal's mechanic]\n\n\u2022 Jang Seo Kyung as Susan [Rugal]\n\n\u2022 Park Choong Seon as Section Chief Oh [Rugal]\n\n\u2022 [[Yoo Sang-joon|Yoo Sang Hoon]] as Min Dal Ho [Argos acting leader]\n\n\u2022 [[Park Jung-hae|Park Jung Hak]] as Go Yong Deok [Assemblyman]\n\n\u2022 [[Kim Jin-woo (musician)|Kim In Woo]] as Choi Yong [Argos]\n\n\u2022 Yoo Ji Yeon as Jang Mi Joo [Argos]\n\n\u2022 Ji Dae Han as Bong Man Cheol [Argos]\n\n\u2022 [[Kim Da-hyun|Kim Da Hyun]] as Seol Min Joon [Argos]\n\n\u2022 [[Lee Do-hyun|Lee Bo Hyun]] as Yang Moon Bok\n\n\u2022 [[Lee Seol|Lee Seo El]] as Yeo Jin [Kang Gi Bum's wife]\n\n\u2022 Dong Hyun Bae as Lee Jae Han\n\n=== Special participation ===\n\u2022 Im Yong Soon as Police (Ep.1)\n\n\u2022 Yoo Hyung Kwan as Goo Won Bong (Ep.1)\n\n\u2022 Kim Yoon Hong as Park No Shik (Ep.1-2)\n\n\u2022 Kim Jong Goo as Politician (Ep. 3)\n\n\u2022 [[Sori (singer)|Kim So Ri]] as Singer\n\n== Production ==\nThe series is directed by Ahn Gil-ho Kang Cheol Woo<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kdramapal.com/first-look-choi-jin-hyuk-park-sung-woong-sci-fi-thriller-rugal/|title=First look at Choi Jin-hyuk, Park Sung-woong in sci-fi thriller 'Rugal'|last=IndoorEnthusiast|date=2020-01-29|website=Kdramapal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://forums.soompi.com/topic/441992-current-drama-2020-rugal-%EB%A3%A8%EA%B0%88-sat-sun-2250-kst/|title=[Current Drama 2020] Rugal, \ub8e8\uac08 - Sat & Sun @ 22:50 KST|website=Soompi Forums|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref> (''The Thousandth Man, Cheo Yong 2: The Paranormal Detective, [[Something About 1%]], [[My Secret Romance]], [[So I Married an Anti-fan (TV series)|So I Married an Anti-Fan]]'')\n\n== Ratings ==\nIn this table, {{color|blue|'''the blue numbers'''}} represent the lowest ratings and {{color|red|'''the red numbers'''}} represent the highest ratings.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! rowspan=\"3\" |{{abbr|Ep.|Episode}}\n! rowspan=\"3\" |Original broadcast date\n! colspan=\"2\" |Average audience share\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |AGB Nielsen<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nielsenkorea.co.kr/tv_terrestrial_day.asp?menu=Tit_1&sub_menu=3_1&area=00|title=Nielsen Korea|work=AGB Nielsen Media Research|language=ko|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601140426/http://www.nielsenkorea.co.kr/tv_terrestrial_day.asp?menu=Tit_1&sub_menu=3_1&area=00|archive-date=June 1, 2016|accessdate=July 6, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! width=\"90\" |Nationwide\n! width=\"90\" |[[Seoul Capital Area|Seoul]]\n|-\n!1\n|March 28, 2020\n| -\n|'''{{Color|Red|2.612%}}'''\n|-\n!2\n|March 29, 2020\n| -\n|'''{{Color|Blue|3.884%}}'''\n|-\n!3\n|April 4, 2020\n| -\n|2.874%\n|-\n!4\n|April 5, 2020\n| -\n|3.199%\n|-\n!5\n|April 11, 2020\n| -\n| -\n|-\n!6\n|April 12, 2020\n| -\n| -\n|-\n!7\n|April 18, 2020\n| -\n| -\n|-\n!8\n|April 19, 2020\n| -\n| -\n|-\n!9\n|April 25, 2020\n| -\n| -\n|-\n!10\n|April 26, 2020\n| -\